{"id":26883,"date":"2018-12-05T12:12:59","date_gmt":"2018-12-05T08:12:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=26883"},"modified":"2023-11-29T15:58:42","modified_gmt":"2023-11-29T11:58:42","slug":"four-powerful-dua","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/12\/05\/four-powerful-dua\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Dua: Four powerful supplications for morning"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Juwayriah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to her one morning for the dawn prayer and she was in the mosque. Then, he returned later in the morning while she was sitting. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>You have not left this position you are in<\/strong>.\u201d She said yes. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>I said four words after you, three times each. If these words were weighed against whatever you said since this morning, it would surely outweigh them: Glory be to Allah and His praise by the number of His creation, by His pleasure, by the weight of His Throne, and by the vastness of His words.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2726<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064f\u0648\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u062e\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u0650\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0628\u064f\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064b \u062d\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0647\u065